<br>
Mez extras, and use Fear and an animation.  Specs are pre-snared for your Fear-Kiting convenience.  Also, passing Orc Priests can be tapped for mana refresh and then fed to your pet.  Good cash here.<br>
<br>
Acrylia Caverns are quite fun for Charm Soloing at 58-60.  Everything there is a hideous miscon, and hits way harder than its level.  They have crappy MR (except for the occasional magic-immune ones they threw in to hose AE groups) and most of them can be tapped for mana.  The zone is almost always empty and it's easy to get singles.  Also, nothing sees through Invis.<br>
<br>
